Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.42,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,侵蝕防護壁啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.74,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,Cross Interleave模式展開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.19,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,比剛才更加強烈的鑽入心裡啊
