Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.12,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.92,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,Nova分離體正在增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.90,Sub1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒完沒了啊
